  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Demonstrate that the Karius Infectious Disease Diagnostic Sequencing Assay performed on
      plasma can accurately detect the microbiologic etiology in febrile allogeneic stem-cell
      transplant patients when compared with standard clinical diagnostics
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
